      "created_at": "2021-11-29T22:28:29.852Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hello,</p>\n<p>I feel stupid asking this but thought I\u2019d ask nonetheless for the avoidance of any doubt and on the off chance that it might help someone else.</p>\n<p>I am using an Elite Direto X smart trainer, iPhone 10 XR, and a chest-strap heart rate monitor.</p>\n<p>When I start a workout (e.g. 30 minute recovery - classics) should I enable both HR mode and ERG mode or just the one?</p>\n<p>On the actual workout, do I just pick one gear and then complete all the stages in that same gear or am I allowed to manually shift gears?</p>\n<p>I\u2019m a new \u2018cyclist\u2019 and still learning so would appreciate any info.</p>",
